          <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 my-auto showcase-text">
            <h2 style="color:white">About</h2>
            <p style="color:white" class="lead mb-0">In this website you can find some of the most popular sneakers and compare their prices on resell websites to see where it is more convinient to buy at.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters">
          <div class="col-lg-6 text-white showcase-img" style="background-image: url('images/pairOfShoes.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="col-lg-6 my-auto showcase-text">
            <h2 style="color:white">Other Stuff</h2>
            <p style="color:white" class="lead mb-0">Other</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters">
          <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 text-white showcase-img" style="background-image: url('images/landingPage.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 my-auto showcase-text">
            <h2 style="color:white">Why</h2>
            <p style="color:white" class="lead mb-0">I created this website because of my love for sneakers and because I wanted to put my skills to the test and create a full on porject using Google Cloud Platform.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
